title: Alexander Wang's Fall '17 Collection Gives You a Lifetime Supply of All-Black Outfit Ideas
text:
Alexander Wang Fall 2017 Collection Alexander Wang's Fall '17 Collection Gives You a Lifetime Supply of All-Black Outfit Ideas February 11, 2017   Alexander Wang's Fall '17 Collection Gives You a Lifetime Supply of All-Black Outfit Ideas 
When you attend an Alexander Wang show, it's an experience you will never forget. For his Fall 2017 collection, the designer brought the fashion crowd to Harlem, unveiling several grunge-inspired looks. If you love to wear all black (like we do) this was what you were waiting for. To add to the excitment, both Bella Hadid and Kendall Jenner took the stage in outfits we wish we could have this Fall. The show in one word was: incredible.
